            <lg xml:id="TK63">
<l>tamporu ḷeṉpatam makka ḷavarporu</l>
<l>ṭantam viṉaiyāṉ varum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>People call their children their wealth; the wealth of their children</l>
<l>comes to each parent according to karma.</l>
